Titolo: Kid A Mnesia Exhibition

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Kid A Mnesia Exhibition is a 2021 exploration game published by Epic Games for macOS, Windows, and PlayStation 5. It serves as a digital exhibition of music and artwork created for the Radiohead albums Kid A (2000) and Amnesiac (2001). It was developed by Namethemachine, Arbitrarily Good Productions and Epic Games, with Radiohead singer Thom Yorke, producer Nigel Godrich and artist Stanley Donwood. 
Kid A Mnesia Exhibition was conceived as a physical installation artwork, but this was canceled by logistical problems and the COVID-19 pandemic. It was announced alongside the compilation album Kid A Mnesia and released 18 November 2021 as a free download. It received positive reviews.

Genere: Exploration 

Valutazione: N/A
